Frequently Asked Questions (FAQs)
1. What is a Russian Manicure?
A Russian manicure, also known as a dry manicure, is a technique that involves meticulous cuticle work and the use of an electric file to achieve perfectly shaped and smooth nails. It is celebrated for its precision and long-lasting results.

2. Why is Code Hair considered the best nail art salon in Dubai ?
Code Hair stands out for its highly skilled technicians, premium products, hygienic environment, and customized nail art services. Their dedication to perfection and customer satisfaction makes them the best choice for nail art in Dubai.

3. What types of nail art can I get at Code Hair?
Code Hair offers a wide range of nail art designs, from minimalist and elegant styles to intricate patterns and bold statements. Their talented nail artists can create customized designs based on your preferences.
